{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01VhapQYo4aeHGi6vXGtXVoN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the source file and convert it to a knowledge file JSON.\n\n**Step 1: Identify the title**\nThe first heading underlined with `=====` is \"応答不要メッセージ受信処理\"\n\n**Step 1.5: Check for no-knowledge-content**\nThe source has clear Layer A and Layer B content - implementation guides, code examples, etc. So `no_knowledge_content: false`.\n\n**Step 2: Build the section list**\nLooking for h2 headings (underlined with `-----`):\n\n1. \"アプリケーション開発者が実装する成果物\" (underlined with `------`)\n\n\n2. \"フォーマット定義ファイル\" (underlined with `----`)\n3. \"一時テーブルの定義\" (underlined with `--`)\n4. \"Formクラス\" (underlined with `----`)\n5. \"SQLファイル\" (underlined with `----`)\n\nNow I'm checking the character counts for each section to see if any need h3 promotion. The first section is relatively short with just a list under 2000 characters, and I'm working through the remaining sections to determine their lengths and structure.\n\nLooking more carefully at the RST formatting, I notice the document uses `=====` for the main title with both overline and underline, then `------` and `----` for h2 sections, with `--` for some items. There's also a subsection \"実際のテーブル定義の例\" that uses `=====` as a single underline. I need to clarify how RST determines heading levels based on the underline characters used throughout the document. I'm working through the RST heading hierarchy now. The document structure uses `=====` with both overline and underline for the main title, then `------` for h2 sections, and `=====` with just an underline for h3 headings like \"実際のテーブル定義の例\" nested within those sections. For the \"一時テーブルの定義\" section, I'm counting the actual text content—around 30 characters for the opening statement about storing received messages in temporary tables by type, then examining the rules that follow.\n\nAll the sections I'm analyzing fall well under 2000 characters of plain text, so no h3 promotion is needed. The document breaks down into five main sections: application developer deliverables, format definition files, temporary table definitions, Form classes, and SQL files.\n\nFor the format definition files, the tool automatically generates them from the external interface design document as input. The temporary table definitions come next in the structure.\n\nNow I'm looking at the rules for temporary tables: they need a primary key column that uniquely identifies each message (which Nablarch handles the numbering for), columns corresponding to each item in the received message, and standard fields like user ID and creation timestamp.\n\nFor the Form class, I need to follow a naming convention based on the request ID, set up the constructor to accept the message sequence and the request message object, and place it in the Async package.\n\nThe configuration for where this Form class lives is specified through the formClassPackage property in MessageReceiveActionSettings.\n\nFor the SQL file, I'm creating a file named after the request ID with an INSERT_ID of \"INSERT_MESSAGE\", and the directory location is controlled by the sqlFilePackageProperty in AsyncMessageReceiveActionSettings.\n\nNow I'm outlining what developers actually need to implement: the format definition file that describes the message layout, a temporary table to store the received message, a Form class to persist it to the database, and the SQL file containing the INSERT statement.\n\nThe format definition file gets generated automatically from the external interface design document using a generation tool. Here's what a sample looks like for user registration data—it specifies the text encoding, record length, and fixed file type, then defines each field with its position and data type.\n\nDefining the message structure fields... 一時テーブルの定義ルール:\n\n- 主キー: 電文を一意に識別するIDカラム。値はNablarchフレームワークで採番する。桁数はプロジェクトの方式設計に従う。\n- 電文の各項目に対応するカラムを属性情報に定義する。\n- プロジェクト方式に合わせて共通項目（登録ユーザID、登録日時など）を定義する。\n\nテーブル定義例では、受信電文連番をCHAR(10)の主キーとして設定し、ログインIDやユーザー名、メールアドレス、電話番号などの属性項目をVARCHAR2やNVARCHAR2で定義している。さらに共通項目も追加する予定だ。\n\nFormクラスの作成ルール:\n\n- クラス名は受信電文のリクエストIDに\"Form\"を付与する。\n- 2引数コンストラクタを定義し、受信電文連番と受信電文オブジェクトを受け取る。\n- パッケージ配置は`AsyncMessageReceiveActionSettings`の`formClassPackage`プロパティで指定される。\n\nコンストラクタ内では、受信電文のボディ部から`RequestMessage#getRecordOf()`を使ってレコードを取得し、各フィールドに値を設定する。\n\nSQLファイル... 完成したSQLの値部分を確認して、参照先のドキュメントをそのまま保持する必要があります。また、検索ヒントとして「応答不要メッセージ受信」や「メッセージ受信処」といったキーワードが関連していることを確認しています。\n\nAsyncMessageReceiveActionやFormクラス、SQLファイルの構成など、実装に必要な各要素の参照先を整理しているところです。\n\n公式ドキュメントのベースURLは空文字列で、ソース内に外部URLがないため、official_doc_urlsは空配列になります。これでJSONの構造を組み立てる準備ができました。\n\nAssembling the JSON output... I'm looking at the structure of a message receiving system with several key components that need to be implemented. The framework handles the core message reception through Nablarch, so the developer needs to focus on the supporting pieces like format definitions, temporary tables for storing received messages, a Form class to map the data, and SQL files for persistence. フォーマット定義ファイルの具体例を示すと、テキストエンコーディングや固定長レコードの仕様を指定した上で、ユーザー登録情報の各フィールドをバイト位置と型で定義していく構造になっている。 Generating the format definition example... I'm outlining what developers need to implement: the format definition file that describes message layout, a temporary table to store messages, a Form class for database registration, and the SQL INSERT statements. The format definition file itself is generated automatically from the external interface design document using a dedicated tool, and I'm showing a sample that defines the text encoding and record structure for a user registration message. Defining the temporary table structure with a primary key for message identification and corresponding columns for each received message field, plus standard project attributes like user ID and creation timestamp. Now I'm looking at the schema for common fields like user IDs and timestamps, then moving into the Form class creation rules where I need to define a constructor that takes the received message sequence and request message object, and place it in the package specified by the AsyncMessageReceiveActionSettings configuration. Now I'm setting up the SQL file configuration, specifying where the SQL files should be stored and showing an example INSERT statement that saves the received message data to a temporary table. Finishing the SQL INSERT statement with the remaining parameter bindings, then I need to format everything as JSON with proper escaping for the output.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":23558,"cache_read_input_tokens":29955,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":23558,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6070e6cb-693f-4f1a-adc5-b34e68f1c5e4","uuid":"ac946a76-730d-4308-89b8-25c778ba05c7"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01VhapQYo4aeHGi6vXGtXVoN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01BbjBXzBFu61FkhxoY9ss5u","name":"StructuredOutput","input":{"id":"mom-messaging-03_mqDelayedReceive","title":"応答不要メッセージ受信処理","no_knowledge_content":false,"official_doc_urls":[],"index":[{"id":"s1","title":"アプリケーション開発者が実装する成果物","hints":["応答不要メッセージ受信","メッセージ受信処理","フォーマット定義ファイル","一時テーブル","Formクラス","SQLファイル","AsyncMessageReceiveAction"]},{"id":"s2","title":"フォーマット定義ファイル","hints":["フォーマット定義ファイル","電文レイアウト","MS932","Fixed","userData","record-length","text-encoding"]},{"id":"s3","title":"一時テーブルの定義","hints":["一時テーブル","受信電文連番","電文保存テーブル","message-save-table","テーブル定義","CHAR","VARCHAR2","NVARCHAR2"]},{"id":"s4","title":"Formクラス","hints":["Formクラス","AsyncMessageReceiveActionSettings","formClassPackage","RequestMessage","DataRecord","getRecordOf","RM11AC0201Form","受信電文連番"]},{"id":"s5","title":"SQLファイル","hints":["SQLファイル","INSERT_MESSAGE","sqlFilePackage","AsyncMessageReceiveActionSettings","INSERT文","受信電文登録"]}],"sections":{"s1":"電文を受信するアクションはNablarchが提供するため（:ref:`messageDelayedReceiveDesign`参照）、アプリケーション開発者が実装する成果物は以下のみ:\n\n- フォーマット定義ファイル（電文のレイアウト定義）\n- 電文を登録する一時テーブルの定義\n- データベースへ電文を登録するFormクラス\n- 電文を登録するINSERT文を記述したSQLファイル","s2":"フォーマット定義ファイルは外部インタフェース設計書を入力として、フォーマット定義ファイル自動生成ツールにより生成する。\n\nサンプル（ユーザ登録情報電文のレイアウト）:\n\n```\ntext-encoding:    \"MS932\"\nrecord-length:    420\nfile-type:        \"Fixed\"\n\n[userData]\n1   loginId                     X(20)\n21  kanjiName                   N(100)\n121 kanaName                    N(100)\n221 ?filler1                    X(50)\n271 mailAddress                 X(100)\n371 extensionNumberBuilding     X(2)\n373 extensionNumberPersonal     X(4)\n377 mobilePhoneNumberAreaCode   X(3)\n380 mobilePhoneNumberCityCode   X(4)\n384 mobilePhoneNumberSbscrCode  X(4)\n388 ?filler2                    X(33)\n```","s3":"一時テーブルの定義ルール:\n\n- 主キー: 電文を一意に識別するIDカラム。値はNablarchフレームワークで採番する。桁数はプロジェクトの方式設計に従う。\n- 受信した電文の各項目に対応するカラムを属性情報に定義する。\n- プロジェクト方式に合わせて共通項目（登録ユーザID、登録日時など）を定義する。\n\n主キー:\n\n| カラム論理名 | 定義 |\n|---|---|\n| 受信電文連番 | CHAR(10) |\n\n属性項目:\n\n| カラム論理名 | 定義 |\n|---|---|\n| ログインID | VARCHAR2(20) |\n| 漢字名称 | NVARCHAR2(100) |\n| カナ名称 | NVARCHAR2(100) |\n| メールアドレス | VARCHAR2(100) |\n| 内線番号(ビル番号) | VARCHAR2(2) |\n| 内線番号(個人番号) | VARCHAR2(4) |\n| 携帯電話番号(市外) | VARCHAR2(3) |\n| 携帯電話番号(市内) | VARCHAR2(4) |\n| 携帯電話番号(加入) | VARCHAR2(4) |\n\n共通項目:\n\n| カラム論理名 | 定義 |\n|---|---|\n| 登録ユーザID | CHAR(10) |\n| 登録日時 | TIMESTAMP |\n| 更新ユーザID | CHAR(10) |\n| 更新日時 | TIMESTAMP |\n| 登録リクエストID | CHAR(10) |\n| 登録実行時ID | CHAR(29) |","s4":"Formクラス作成ルール:\n\n- クラス名: 受信電文のリクエストID + \"Form\"\n- コンストラクタ: `(String receivedMessageSequence, nablarch.fw.messaging.RequestMessage message)` の2引数コンストラクタを定義すること\n  - `String`: 受信電文連番\n  - `RequestMessage`: 受信電文\n- 配置パッケージ: `AsyncMessageReceiveActionSettings` の `formClassPackage` プロパティに設定されたパッケージ\n\n```xml\n<component name=\"asyncMessageReceiveActionSettings\"\n           class=\"nablarch.fw.messaging.action.AsyncMessageReceiveActionSettings\">\n  <property name=\"formClassPackage\" value=\"nablarch.sample.messaging.form\" />\n</component>\n```\n\nコンストラクタ実装例（電文ボディの取得）:\n\n```java\npublic RM11AC0201Form(String receivedMessageSequence, RequestMessage message) {\n    this.receivedMessageSequence = receivedMessageSequence;\n    // 電文のボディ部はRequestMessage#getRecordOf(<レコード名>)で取得\n    // レコード名はフォーマット定義ファイルで設定したレコード名称を指定する\n    DataRecord data = message.getRecordOf(\"userData\");\n    loginId = data.getString(\"loginId\");\n    kanjiName = data.getString(\"kanjiName\");\n    kanaName = data.getString(\"kanaName\");\n    mailAddress = data.getString(\"mailAddress\");\n    extensionNumberBuilding = data.getString(\"extensionNumberBuilding\");\n    // 以下、各フィールドに設定\n}\n```","s5":"SQLファイル作成ルール:\n\n- ファイル名: 受信電文のリクエストID + \".sql\"\n- SQL_ID: `INSERT_MESSAGE`\n- 配置ディレクトリ: `AsyncMessageReceiveActionSettings` の `sqlFilePackage` プロパティに設定されたディレクトリ\n\n```xml\n<component name=\"asyncMessageReceiveActionSettings\"\n    class=\"nablarch.fw.messaging.action.AsyncMessageReceiveActionSettings\">\n  <property name=\"sqlFilePackage\" value=\"nablarch.sample.messaging.sql\" />\n</component>\n```\n\nSQL例（:ref:`一時テーブル<message-save-table>`へのINSERT）:\n\n```sql\nINSERT_MESSAGE =\nINSERT INTO USER_INFO_RECEIVE_MESSAGE (\n    RECEIVED_MESSAGE_SEQUENCE,\n    LOGIN_ID,\n    KANJI_NAME,\n    KANA_NAME,\n    MAIL_ADDRESS,\n    EXTENSION_NUMBER_BUILDING,\n    EXTENSION_NUMBER_PERSONAL,\n    MOBILE_PHONE_NUMBER_AREA_CODE,\n    MOBILE_PHONE_NUMBER_CITY_CODE,\n    MOBILE_PHONE_NUMBER_SBSCR_CODE,\n    STATUS,\n    INSERT_USER_ID,\n    INSERT_DATE,\n    INSERT_REQUEST_ID,\n    INSERT_EXECUTION_ID,\n    UPDATED_USER_ID,\n    UPDATED_DATE\n    )\n    VALUES\n    (\n    :receivedMessageSequence,\n    :loginId,\n    :kanjiName,\n    :kanaName,\n    :mailAddress,\n    :extensionNumberBuilding,\n    :extensionNumberPersonal,\n    :mobilePhoneNumberAreaCode,\n    :mobilePhoneNumberCityCode,\n    :mobilePhoneNumberSbscrCode,\n    '0',\n    :insertUserId,\n    :insertDate,\n    :insertRequestId,\n    :updatedUserId,\n    :updatedDate\n    )\n```"}}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":23558,"cache_read_input_tokens":29955,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":23558,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6070e6cb-693f-4f1a-adc5-b34e68f1c5e4","uuid":"56cf804c-ba53-469e-8d3c-956a71509f22"}
